---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
import InfoPageShell from "../components/InfoPageShell.astro";

const title = "Privacy";
const description = "Lucia's Dictionary stores wordbook items, settings, and lookup caches in the browser and does not provide accounts, public profiles, or advertising tracking.";
---

<MainLayout title={title} description={description} canonicalPath="/privacy/" ogTitle={title} appScript={false}>
  <InfoPageShell title="Privacy" titleZh="隐私与数据" current="privacy">
    <p>
      Lucia's Dictionary is designed as a simple local-first learning tool. It does not provide accounts, public user
      profiles, search-history sharing, personalized advertising, or a backend wordbook sync feature.
    </p>
    <section>
      <h2>Browser Storage</h2>
      <p>
        Saved words, settings, daily-use state, and lookup caches are stored in the current browser through localStorage.
        Clearing browser data or using another device can remove or separate that local data.
      </p>
    </section>
    <section>
      <h2>Network Requests</h2>
      <p>
        Most English word cards use bundled data. When local data is not enough, a word may be requested from
        dictionaryapi.dev and its definition may be translated through Google's translation fallback. Chinese sentence
        input checks the local phrasebook first and only uses the translation fallback when no local match is available.
      </p>
      <p>
        Photo OCR compresses the selected image in the browser, sends it to the same-origin <code>/api/ocr</code>
        endpoint, and forwards it to OCR.Space. The app does not save the uploaded image or OCR result on its server, and
        OCR responses are marked <code>no-store</code>. Cloudflare may process operational security and performance data
        while serving the site and API.
      </p>
    </section>
    <section>
      <h2>Children's Information</h2>
      <p>
        The public site should not publish private child information such as schools, addresses, birth dates, schedules,
        private photographs, or account details.
      </p>
    </section>
    <section>
      <h2>Your Controls</h2>
      <p>
        You can clear lookup caches from Settings, remove individual saved words, clear the wordbook, export it as JSON,
        or clear this site's browser data. Do not upload photographs that contain private child information when a typed
        sentence is sufficient.
      </p>
    </section>
  </InfoPageShell>
</MainLayout>
